        \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000366_fr2.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"rear\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000366_fr1_rear_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 13.05.2016\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000366_fr1_rear.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 13.05.2016\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000366_fr2_rear.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 14.10.2016\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#AA\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>C\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ai\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> Po\u003Cunclear>m\u003C/unclear>pei Felic\u003Chi rend=\"small\">i\u003C/hi>s\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>et Sc\u003Cunclear>r\u003C/unclear>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ib\u003C/supplied>oniae \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> Resti\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\" break=\"no\"/>\u003Cunclear>t\u003C/unclear>utae \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text based upon photograph, after Korhonen\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>(tomb) of Gaius Pompeius Felix and Scribonia Restituta\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>Given that both names reflect senatorial families attested in the area, this is assumed to be a freedman and freedwoman of the families. Korhonen notes the absence of 'Dis Manibus' as encouraging a first-century date, alongside the palaeography. Castelli and Ferrara report the right fragment only as a separate text, in addition to reporting the entire text, following a notice in Amico.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\">7084\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Amico\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1741\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>225 no.29\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F5INCW3T\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Castelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1769\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>182 no. 102 (269 no.46)\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/SPTB56H3\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Castelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1784\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>192 no. 117 (288 no.47)\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/7PSFHSUH\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ferrara\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1829\u003C/date> \n              